Map {
User Stories {
Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view orders that are not supported by the Water Sports application.

Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select a travel time for my water sports activity.

View Available Activities: As a user, I want to be able to view the available activities offered by the Water Sports application.

Book Activities: As a user, I want to be able to book activities offered by the Water Sports application.

View Booked Activities: As a user, I want to be able to view the activities I have booked through the Water Sports application.

Cancel Booked Activities: As a user, I want to be able to cancel activities I have booked through the Water Sports application.

Payment Options: As a user, I want to be able to view the payment options available for booking activities through the Water Sports application.

View Reviews: As a user, I want to be able to view reviews of activities offered by the Water Sports application.

Leave Reviews: As a user, I want to be able to leave reviews of activities offered by the Water Sports application.

}

Administrator Stories {

Manage Activities: As an administrator, I want to be able to manage the activities offered by the Water Sports application.

Manage Bookings: As an administrator, I want to be able to manage the bookings made through the Water Sports application.

Manage Reviews: As an administrator, I want to be able to manage the reviews left by users of the Water Sports application.

}

}
